#: org.kde.audiotube.appdata.xml:125
msgid ""
"AudioTube can search YouTube Music, list albums and artists, play "
"automatically generated playlists, albums and allows to put your own "
"playlist together. It is adapted to mobile phones and desktop computers."
msgstr ""
"AudioTube dapat mencari YouTube Music, daftar album dan artis, putar "
"playlist yang dibuat secara otomatis, album dan memungkinkan Anda untuk "
"menyusun playlist Anda sendiri. Aplikasi ini disesuaikan untuk ponsel dan "
"komputer desktop."

